NAME

DateTime::Locale::lg_UG - Locale data examples for the Ganda Uganda (lg-UG) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Ganda Uganda locale.

Date Formats

Full

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = Lwakubiri, 5 Febwaliyo 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = Lwakutaano, 22 Desemba 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = Lwamukaaga, 15 Sebuttemba -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Febwaliyo 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Desemba 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 Sebuttemba -10

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Feb 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Des 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 Seb -10

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 05/02/2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22/12/1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15/09/-10
